{"tid":1461083,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"今次連登嘅更新直接收咗五毛三毛皮","createTime":"2019-08-13T06:09:54.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-13T09:55:13.000Z","uid":291448,"like":50,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":41,"replies":[{"pid":"f80d2763e8b32264085d21706d064ea5b693fc29","tid":1461083,"uid":291448,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T06:09:54.000Z","msg":"今次連登嘅更新主要係針對住P牌仔黎進行調整 <br />\n由2019 年 6 月後註冊嘅人一律<span style=\"color: red;\">標示 P 牌直至另行通知</span>，即係代表D五毛三毛如果最近開AC 就會一直P牌落去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n至於2019 年 6 月前註冊嘅人上線日數未滿 90 天就會標示 P 牌 90日後P牌就會消失<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n其實P牌都唔算係一個問題 D五毛三毛照樣都會帶到風向<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 所以有見及此 連仔做左樣嘢黎杜絕大部份五毛三毛帶風向 就係限制P牌仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />係連登嘅功能<br />\n<br />\n1.<span style=\"color: red;\">每天只可開設一個主題</span> <br />\n2<span style=\"color: red;\">.所有回覆強制無「推文」效果，除會員在回覆時手動開啟「不推文回覆」外，將不會於內文中作出（手掌圖）標示</span><br />\n3.<span style=\"color: red;\">無法對所有主題或回覆作出評分。</span><br />\n<br />\n淨係2同3嘅限制就已經足以收咗五毛三毛皮 佢哋冇辦法再推分化post 冇辦法比正負皮帶風向<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />開幾多AC都冇用<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">五毛三毛係時候收皮啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n</span></span></span>"},{"pid":"5a411a0adcfc2940d4bb0d4575553e1b1a822e2a","tid":1461083,"uid":291448,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T06:11:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />88五毛三毛"},{"pid":"f9f59212db55c93d3935e8c41f591ea7f11e62c4","tid":1461083,"uid":291448,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T06:12:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"efa391c878118f92b9fc9fdc99783c1c51ef87b9","tid":1461083,"uid":249341,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T06:14:54.000Z","msg":"五毛死全家<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />共產黨嘅走狗"},{"pid":"fa99bbc6ff5eb75346b41038259b3304676d2b49","tid":1461083,"uid":291448,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T06:15:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9650abe1886526b23d01ce0477a41728c512df8f","tid":1461083,"uid":258208,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T06:17:20.000Z","msg":"P牌仔表示完全贊成<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"95e486cd4c78b230b030746b57dfe063dea9fc6b","tid":1461083,"uid":291448,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"9650abe1886526b23d01ce0477a41728c512df8f","tid":1461083,"uid":258208,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T06:17:20.000Z","msg":"P牌仔表示完全贊成<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkg